nomination next month at the Democratic National Convention in Los
Angeles.
</P>
<P>
Gore's Republican rival Bush, who also spoke at the same
convention Monday, acknowledged his party's history with black
Americans was not good and promised to do better, but he did not
specify how to combat racism.  
