their counterparts from five other countries and asked to decipher
one percent of the human genome sequencing.
</P>
<P>
China is the only developing country to participate in the
project, he said.
</P>
<P>
China has rich gene resources, and the success of the HGP will
contribute greatly to the medical, biological, and pharmaceutical
sciences.
</P>
