hotel rooms booked through the network increased by three to four
times on a yearly basis in the first half of this year.
</P>
<P>
Sources say that the CTS will open a website within this month.
</P>
<P>
And the CYTS has also opened a website, www.cytsonline.com, in
order to expand business by means of e-commerce.  
