The four sub-indices reaped across-the-aboard gains, with
Finance, Utilities, Properties and Industry &AMP; Commerce rising by
2.30 percent, 0.62 percent, 0.46 percent and 0.75 percent,
respectively.
</P>
<P>
The Hang Seng China Enterprises Index gained 7.49 percent, and
the Hang Seng China-Affiliated Corp Index went up 1.76 percent.
</P>
<P>
The Hang Seng IT Index went up 0.09 percent and the Hang Seng
IT Portfolio Index up 2.30 percent.  
